---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Solutions" description="Media solutions from Future Media — radio, digital, outdoor, and integrated campaigns.">
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Solutions</h1>
      <p>End-to-end media solutions for brands that want to be heard, seen, and remembered.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="container page-content__inner">
      <p>Future Media delivers comprehensive media solutions that span the entire consumer journey. From the moment someone turns on the radio in the morning to the billboard they pass on their commute, we ensure your brand is part of their day.</p>

      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-card__icon">📻</div>
          <h3>Radio Solutions</h3>
          <p>Spots, sponsorships, live reads, and branded content across our station portfolio.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-card__icon">🎬</div>
          <h3>Content Production</h3>
          <p>Podcast, video, and social content from our in-house studio at Hyper Motor City.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-card__icon">📊</div>
          <h3>Media Planning</h3>
          <p>Data-driven campaign planning with audience insights and performance tracking.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-card__icon">🏟️</div>
          <h3>Event Activation</h3>
          <p>Live brand experiences, sponsorships, and on-ground activations at major events.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-card__icon">🖥️</div>
          <h3>Digital Campaigns</h3>
          <p>Social media, display, streaming, and influencer partnerships across platforms.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-card__icon">🗺️</div>
          <h3>Outdoor Network</h3>
          <p>Premium billboard, transit, and street furniture across Namibia's key markets.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p><a href="/advertise/solutions" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top: 16px; display: inline-flex;">Explore advertising solutions</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
